Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:08.86,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side,,1830,0,0,,于我心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.41,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side,,1830,0,0,,无论何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.62,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side,,1830,0,0,,两人一起　乘风破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:18.39,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}这份坚不可摧的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:25.50,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}独一无二不可替代　是因为你呀
